Biography. Alex Amouyel is the President and CEO of Newman's Own Foundation and the Author of The Answer is You: A Guidebook to Creating a Life Full of Impact.
Newman's Own Foundation has announced Alex Amouyel as its incoming President and Chief Executive Officer, starting in April.
